Status of your 5 recommendations:
1. **Drop messages_backup** — ✅ Yes, confirmed stale. Fix script in the report.
2. **Queue-depth index** — ✅ Already in migration_004_message_bus.sql (the PostgreSQL migration I wrote earlier).
3. **TTL cleanup** — ✅ Already in migration_004 (NOTIFY-based retention + cleanup).
